title: Hermes Click 16
description: Hermes Click 16 crossbody bag in light blue Chevre leather (Y: 2020). Featuring gold-toned hardware, single detachable leather shoulder strap, and Hermès 'click' closure on frontal flap. This opens to a matching colour leather interior with four card slots and two patch pockets. Approximate dimensions: 16cm(L) x 14cm(H) x 2.5cm(D), strap drop 56cm. Accompanied by Hermès dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
